		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/07/07/today-in-small-business-factory-man/" data-title="Today in Small Business: &#8216;Factory Man&#8217;" data-description="How to get people to reply to your emails. The value of cyber insurance. And seven things you do not want to hear about small-business tax deductions.">
