				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Privately held construction companies are <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/sageworks/2014/07/06/private-businesses-build-on-constructions-growth/">increasing sales</a> at an annual rate of 13 percent, marking a second year of double-digit growth.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here&#8217;s how a deli turned into a <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/07/06/business/at-zingermans-pastrami-and-partnership-to-go.html">community of nine businesses</a> with 650 employees and $50 million in combined sales.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here is how three entrepreneurs <a href="//www.blogtrepreneur.com/2014/07/03/made-america-3-entrepreneurs-making-businesses-work-usa/">are making</a> their products in the United States.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">And &#8220;<a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/07/06/business/a-game-of-chairs-and-globalization.html?">Factory Man</a>&#8221; tells the story of a furniture maker who battled a Chinese industry, stayed local and helped save an American town. <span id="more-87036"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Government Contracts<br />
</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The experiences of two companies that work on the overhaul of nuclear-powered aircraft carriers illustrate <a href="//www.dailypress.com/business/ports/dp-nws-aircraft-carrier-refueling-sidebar-20140705,0,5568221.story">the ups and downs</a> of being a small contractor.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Advertising</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here&#8217;s how Twitter has attracted online ads and <a href="//nyti.ms/1rCauF1">turned up the revenue</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This is not a difficult daughter, <a href="//digg.com/video/youll-think-this-daughter-is-just-being-difficult-until-the-very-end">just a great</a> ad.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Entrepreneurship</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The 2014 <a href="//smallbiztrends.com/2014/07/2014-small-business-book-awards-winners.html">Small Business Book Awards</a> are announced.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A college dropout <a href="//nypost.com/2014/07/05/the-22-year-old-dropout-who-created-nycs-most-exclusive-credit-card/">has created</a> New York Cityâs âmost exclusiveâ credit card.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A program in Kansas <a href="//cjonline.com/news/local/2014-07-05/program-matches-retiring-business-owners-younger-entrepreneurs">matches</a> retiring business owners with young entrepreneurs.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Online</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here&#8217;s how to get <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/get-people-to-reply-to-your-email-2014-7">people to reply</a> to your emails.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ As gourmet bloggers <a href="//www.fastcolabs.com/3031717/the-technology-behind-food-porn-boom">build more</a> sophisticated sites, more and more eaters (and investors) are taking notice.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A North Carolina business owner <a href="//www.knoxnews.com/news/2014/jul/06/taking-a-small-business-from-a-storefront-to/">has no regrets</a> about closing her store and taking her business online.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/article/235355">next big thing</a> for businesses is cyber insurance.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the Country</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A Michigan <a href="//www.mlive.com/living/grand-rapids/index.ssf/2014/07/grand_rapids_couple_designs_ec.html">couple designs</a> an eco-friendly alternative to wrapping paper.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The fight to<a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/07/06/us/an-everglades-landmark-confronts-the-end-of-the-road.html"> save a general store</a> in the Everglades.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the World</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ According to the Good Country Index, Ireland is the nation that <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/7/6/5871281/ireland-is-the-goodest-of-all-countries-and-the-us-might-be-21st">does the most good</a> for the world, out of 125 nations analyzed.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A Finnish couple <a href="//www.times-standard.com/business/ci_26094712/finnish-couple-wins-quirky-wife-carrying-race">narrowly wins</a> the 19th World Wife Carrying Championships.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A service in England will <a href="//www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/life/relationships/article4140359.ece">rent you a friend</a> if you need one.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Security <a href="//www.nbcnews.com/news/world/u-s-tightens-security-electronics-overseas-airports-n149186">is tightened</a> for some flights coming into the United States.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Taxes</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ You probably <a href="//blog.shoeboxed.com/7-things-dont-want-hear-small-business-deductions/9768/">donât want to hear</a> these seven things about small-business deductions.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Cash Flow</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A capital manager says the <a href="//www.peridotcapital.com/2014/06/profitless-amazon-myth-lives-on-thanks-to-lazy-financial-media.html">relevant metric</a> for Amazon (or any other company) when measuring profitability is operating cash flow.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Technology</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ How IBM is <a href="//qz.com/230689/how-ibm-is-using-big-data-to-fix-beijings-pollution-crisis/">using big data</a> to address Beijingâs pollution crisis.</p>
